            <h2 class="cursive-accent">01 // manifesto</h2>
            <h1>the philosophy of human-made software</h1>

            <div class="detail-block">
                <h3>the challenge of noise</h3>
                <p>
                    today's digital landscape is saturated with automated noise. applications
                    often prioritize engagement over utility, and computation over craftsmanship.
                    at **infiniware**, we reject the notion that software should be a generic
                    commodity. we believe it should be a deliberate expression of human thought.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-lg);">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>clarity over complexity</h3>
                    <p>
                        complexity is the enemy of focus. we build tools that respect your
                        attention. no clutter, no unnecessary features, no "growth hacking."
                        just functional software that does exactly what it says it does,
                        without demanding more than it needs.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h3>transparency as foundation</h3>
                    <p>
                        our systems are open, our logic is clear, and our intentions are honest.
                        we build for the developer and the user who value knowing the mechanics
                        behind their tools. transparency isn't just a policy; it's our backbone.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h3>the silent design language</h3>
                    <p>
                        design should not scream for your attention. it should provide a calm,
                        highly-structured environment where the focus remains on the content
                        and the task at hand. we use spacing, alignment, and typography as
                        structural elements, not decoration.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h3>privacy by default</h3>
                    <p>
                        data is a significant liability, not an asset to be harvested. we collect
                        the absolute minimum required to provide our services. we don't track
                        your movement; we facilitate your productivity.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-xl human-touch">
                <p>
                    infiniware is a testament to what a single developer can achieve when focus
                    is prioritized over expansion. every line is curated.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
